{"tid":334631,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"鮮果芝士撻(附食譜)","createTime":"2017-07-25T01:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T06:33:02.000Z","uid":128531,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76d25b0ad9243719c486d32b83f901de05b17674","tid":334631,"uid":128531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T01:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/083134_bcb6644ae7427416633b51fe3064e0d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F083134_bcb6644ae7427416633b51fe3064e0d1.jpg&h=2bf03278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n份量4個<br />\n材料:<br />\n撻皮<br />\n無鹽牛油31g<br />\n低筋麵粉62g<br />\n糖霜22g<br />\n雞蛋12g<br />\n鹽 少許<br />\n<br />\n餡<br />\n室溫忌廉芝士 125克<br />\n糖 3湯匙<br />\n<br />\n做法<br />\n1.室溫軟化既牛油用電動打蛋器打成羽毛狀<br />\n2.加入糖霜，<br />\n用手動打蛋器將糖霜同牛油混合<br />\n否則糖霜會飛到周圍都有<br />\n3.將蛋液打散加少少鹽，<br />\n分次少量加入牛油內<br />\n(每次都需要將牛油同蛋液攪拌至完全融合)<br />\n4.篩入低筋麵粉，用刮刀攪拌至牛油同麵粉完全混合，用保鮮紙包好雪一小時<br />\n5.將冷藏過既麵團擀成片狀<br />\n6.將撻皮覆蓋在撻模上，並用手指按壓撻皮令佢貼合撻模<br />\n7.係撻皮中間用叉拮啲窿仔<br />\n（避免底部受熱時，撻底凸起）<br />\n8.放入已預熱170度既焗爐，<br />\n用上下火，放中層焗25分鐘<br />\n9.將室溫忌廉芝士用電動打蛋器打至軟身。<br />\n然後加入砂糖，打至糖溶化，顔色淡黃色。<br />\n10.將芝士餡放進撻皮中直至九分滿，放上生果。<br />\n放入雪櫃雪2小時即可享用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bafbd169f19676a5160cc341583a1ee83c7ee6","tid":334631,"uid":30212,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T01:51:07.000Z","msg":"即係免焗？"},{"pid":"9459ab08348aee4389c134ddea12379b1e27685d","tid":334631,"uid":128531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T01:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係免焗？</blockquote><br />\n上面有寫焗25分鐘"},{"pid":"d1c7d3ae40814b1fe070dd93dc6419afa7d57c1f","tid":334631,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"想食你塊撻多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8ce174741d38eff71dbb69eb73d6e21cfb1385","tid":334631,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T02:35:00.000Z","msg":"幾好，之後請繼續開post 介紹其他甜品"},{"pid":"0dd272cd102611972b8cb4083d00cdb6bf90deec","tid":334631,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"我見街賣果啲果撻 <br />\n面頭會揸一層令令地好似啫喱咁既透明物體<br />\n係令啲生果唔會抽乾水定純粹美觀啲？"},{"pid":"81f30dfd7d2f478df317fe3e9bed02d432c051ec","tid":334631,"uid":128531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見街賣果啲果撻 <br />\n面頭會揸一層令令地好似啫喱咁既透明物體<br />\n係令啲生果唔會抽乾水定純粹美觀啲？</blockquote><br />\n果層係鏡面果膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鏡面果膠可以令水果保持濕度<br />\n顏色保持亮澤<br />\n同埋將水果定型"},{"pid":"2f451a064245e961d08f9cc08839972feba8b1ba","tid":334631,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:33:02.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}